documentation:
convert multimodal content list to string
e.g.
    "content": [
        {
            "type": "image",
            "image": "https://qianwen-res.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Qwen-VL/assets/demo.jpeg",
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Describe this image."
        },
    ]
to:
    <|vision_start|><|image_pad|><|vision_end|>Describe this image.
